EN: I love to eat authentic Sichuan cuisine, such as mapo tofu and spicy chicken stir-fry noodles.

ZH: 这家餐厅的炒菜技术很高超，每一道菜都非常美味。
EN: The stir-fry skills of this restaurant are superb, every dish is very delicious.

ZH: 妈妈会经常用高温火候炒菜，使菜肴更加鲜嫩可口。
EN: My mother often uses high heat to stir-fry the food, making the dishes more tender and delicious.

ZH: 我喜欢在家自己动手学习炒菜，尝试各种不同的烹饪方法。
EN: I like to learn how to stir-fry at home myself, trying various cooking methods.

ZH: 这道红烧肉是用老抽和生抽调味后炒制而成的。
EN: This braised pork dish is stir-fried with dark and light soy sauce.

ZH: 他们的炒饭用的是剩饭炒出来的，味道特别香。
EN: Their fried rice is made from leftover rice, it tastes very fragrant.

ZH: 炒菜时要注意火候，以保持食材的营养和口感。
EN: When stir-frying, pay attention to the heat to maintain the nutrition and texture of the ingredients.

